{"product_id":"hoia-superserum-sundrops-30ml","title":"HOIA Superserum Sundrops 30ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSundrops Superserum is a luxurious blend of fast absorbing oils, which gives your face a subtle suntouched complexion and keeps your skin healthy and glowing. Superserum helps to protect skin from environmental stress and it has a natural sunblock, estimated at SPF 25.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSundrops is enriched with more than 10 skin-improving fatty acids and potent blend of organic essential oils with powerful anti-aging effects. This blend reduces the appearance of fine lines, tones, tightens and firms your skin, improves its texture, complexion and elasticity, it also alleviates sunburnt skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e A\u003cspan\u003epply 3 drops on face and massage until absorbed. Sundrops can be used as a  sunblock during the day, or as a repairing face serum during the night. Keep the product from direct sunlight and keep under +25C.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eRubus Idaeus Seed Oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, *Vaccinium Macrocarpon Seed Oil, Squalane, *Nigella Sativa Seed Oil, Dunaliella Salina Extract, *Daucus Carota Sativa Seed Oil, *Commiphora Myrrha Oil, *Fusanus Spicatus Wool Oil, *Lavandula Angustifolia Flower oil, **Geraniol, **Linalool, **Limonene. *Organic. **Natural components of essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104790577479,"sku":null,"price":27.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-superserum-sundrops-30ml-597589.png?v